@startuml
actor "Администратор" as Admin
participant "FeedbackController" as Ctrl
participant "FeedbackService" as Svc
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

Admin -> Ctrl: GET /api/feedback (Bearer JWT Admin)
Ctrl -> Svc: GetAllAsync()
Svc -> DB: SELECT * FROM feedback ORDER BY created_at DESC
DB --> Svc: feedback list
Svc --> Ctrl: Result.Ok(List<FeedbackListItemDto>)
Ctrl --> Admin: 200 OK JSON
@enduml
